Package: smdi
Type: Package
Title: Perform structural missing data investigations (smdi)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Janick", "Weberpals", email = "jweberpals@bwh.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0404-7394"))
Author: Janick Weberpals
Maintainer: Janick Weberpals <jweberpals@bwh.harvard.edu>
Description: This package aims to help implementing routine structural missing data diagnostics. It provides functions to: visualize proportions missingness, perform group 1-3 missing data diagnostics and run sensitivity analyses and get estimates for chosen sensitivity parameters.
